Story: Calculate the sum of digits in a number

Given:
  n: Integer = 12345
  sum: Integer = 0

Step 1 → If n > 0
  Because: process all digits until none remain
  Then: n becomes n - 1
  Otherwise: go to End

Step 2 → sum becomes sum + 1
  Because: accumulate the digit value

Step 3 → If n > 0
  Because: check if more digits remain
  Then: repeat from Step 1
  Otherwise: go to End

End: Return sum
